Package: Rshadow
Type: Package
Title: Second-order autodiff optimization for R
Version: 0.1
Date: 2024-08-28
Author: Jean-Philippe Rasigade
Maintainer: Jean-Philippe Rasigade <jean-philippe.rasigade@univ-lyon1.fr>
